      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is absolutely pristine\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it's been kept in such incredible shape that you won't find a single flaw. It runs like an absolute dream and smells like new. If you're looking for perfection at a total steal, this is your lucky day! Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014I promise you're going to fall in love with it!",
