    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six. The powertrain remains flawlessly aspirated through six individual throttle bodies, with the dual VANOS system fully overhauled for optimal cam timing. The chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock. This specimen boasts a documented rod bearing service and a suspension geometry optimized via Bilstein PSS10 coilovers. With zero bolster wear and a flawless undercarriage, this is a turn-key collector-grade icon.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
