    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior is finished in its original factory paint, which retains a deep, mirror-like shine entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every piece of glass is crystal clear, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash whatsoever. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple, still carrying a faint new-car scent, while the dashboard and wood trim are free of any sun-fading or hairline cracks. All technological features, including the navigation system and premium audio, operate with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. We have a complete binder of service records and original documentation. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and seeks a vehicle that requires absolutely zero compromises.",
